thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Rob & Erin

author: Rob & Erin
title: Rob & Erin
text: We couldn't be happier with the service David & Richard provided during the sale campaign of our property. They were in touch after every open for inspection and kept us up to date along the way. We were interstate for the auction and felt 100% comfortable leaving the sale in David & Richards hands. And what an amazing result they got for us!!! We could not be happier with their services and will use these guys for future property purchases and sales.
